The paper proposes a deep learning architecture for transfer learning, which is a common topic in machine learning and artificial intelligence. The use of deep learning models suggests that the paper could belong to cs.LG (Machine Learning) or cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). The focus on transfer learning and the use of multiple source tasks suggest that the paper could also belong to cs.RO (Robotics) or cs.SY (Systems and Control). Finally, the mention of empirical evaluations on different learning algorithms suggests that the paper could also belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision).
